<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11317</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18522</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>美罗城大酒店正在举办一场盛大的舞会。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18523</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22993</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>城里最富有的人都在这里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22994</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29434</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“多好的舞会啊！”一个戴着钻石项链的女人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33226</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是啊。”另一个女人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33227</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37660</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的礼服上有一颗巨大的红宝石。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37661</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43656</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，一声巨响。轰隆隆！轰隆隆！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43657</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48289</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我听到了摩托车的声音。”一个男人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48290</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53929</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一道电光闪过！嗞！灯熄灭了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53930</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当灯光再次亮起时，大家都开始尖叫起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64325</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们的珠宝！”一个女人大喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64326</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68791</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“被人偷走了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68792</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75579</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇！”杰克说，“火星，看得好清楚啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75580</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80382</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西和朋友们在杰克家的后院里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80383</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84306</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们在玩儿杰克的新望远镜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84307</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87761</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“能让我看一下吗？”玛拉问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87762</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90465</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然。”杰克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90466</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93565</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把望远镜让给了玛拉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93566</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96927</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我看见火星了！”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96928</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101177</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它是红色的，有很多石头！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101178</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106771</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你看到火星人了吗？”特勒尔笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106772</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109521</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哈哈！”玛拉也笑了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109522</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112187</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我没看到火星人！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112188</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117130</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克翻开了一本关于宇宙的书。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117131</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120788</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“接下来，我们找这个星系吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120789</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125467</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他指着一张色彩丰富的图片。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128859</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好酷！”特勒尔说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128860</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132312</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们先要在星图上找到它。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132313</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137915</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔打开星图。罗西靠过去看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137916</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141567</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要在这两颗星星之间找。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146128</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她指着星图上两颗明亮的星星说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146129</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152984</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好的。”杰克说。他在天空上找到了那两颗星星。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158091</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉把望远镜转到有星星的方向。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158092</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162172</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当宇航员一定很酷。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162173</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165390</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想坐火箭上太空！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165391</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169380</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“宇航员是很酷。”特勒尔说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169381</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，你知道谁比宇航员更酷吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178306</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“让我猜猜。”罗西说，“火箭女孩儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178307</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182061</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对！”特勒尔咧嘴笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182062</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186381</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“宇航员需要火箭才能进入太空，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186382</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189713</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是火箭女孩儿不用。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189714</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195181</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧，不过我还是觉得宇航员非常酷。”罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195182</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197782</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔眼睛一亮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197783</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿也许现在正在太空飞行呢！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206781</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们应该用望远镜去找找她！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206782</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西笑了。“我觉得火箭女孩儿现在不在天上。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213387</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217382</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，她的手表响了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217383</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222297</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她悄悄离开朋友们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222298</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232742</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“布洛姆市长。”罗西小声说，“有什么事吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232743</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236715</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，火箭女孩儿。”市长说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236716</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241106</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“出大事儿了！有人偷了珠宝展！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241107</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所有的珠宝——钻石，红宝石，珍珠，都被偷走了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251376</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别担心，市长先生。”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251377</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257456</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿会找到小偷的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>